d five speakers\u003c/a\u003e located below the screen to track your head and beam sound directly to your ears. The feature eliminates the need to keep your head positioned in a sweet spot for optimal sound, and it could be ideal for gamers who are constantly moving around in the heat of battle. The monitor also features a 120Hz refresh rate, a 0.03ms response time, and will launch in the US on May 22nd, 2025, for $799.99.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/6/24337124/bird-buddy-wonder-petal-camera-track-plants-insects-ces-2025\"\u003eWonder plant and insect camera\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Zoom\" tabindex=\"0\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 744px\" srcset=\"https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2522x1776/376x265/filters:focal(1261x888:1262x889):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25820351/Screenshot_2025_01_06_at_6.58.04_PM.png 376w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2522x1776/384x270/filters:focal(1261x888:1262x889):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25820351/Screenshot_2025_01_06_at_6.58.04_PM.png 384w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2522x1776/415x292/filters:focal(1261x888:1262x889):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25820351/Screenshot_2025_01_06_at_6.58.04_PM.png 415w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2522x1776/480x338/filters:focal(1261x888:1262x889):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25820351/Screenshot_2025_01_06_at_6.58.04_PM.png 480w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2522x1776/540x380/filters:focal(1261x888:1262x889):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25820351/Screenshot_2025_01_06_at_6.58.04_PM.png 540w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2522x1776/640x451/filters:foc