080/filters:focal(1920x1080:1921x1081):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25815999/Nitro_Blaze_11_GN7112U_lifestyle_2.jpg 1920w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:3840x2160/2048x1152/filters:focal(1920x1080:1921x1081):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25815999/Nitro_Blaze_11_GN7112U_lifestyle_2.jpg 2048w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:3840x2160/2400x1350/filters:focal(1920x1080:1921x1081):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25815999/Nitro_Blaze_11_GN7112U_lifestyle_2.jpg 2400w\" src=\"https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:3840x2160/2400x1350/filters:focal(1920x1080:1921x1081):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25815999/Nitro_Blaze_11_GN7112U_lifestyle_2.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\"/\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Acer\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eHow big is \u003cem\u003etoo\u003c/em\u003e big for a handheld gaming machine? The answer might be \u003ca href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/6/24335423/acer-handheld-gaming-pc-nitro-blaze-8-11-specs-price\"\u003eAcer’s new Nitro Blaze 11 featuring a beefy 10.95-inch 144 Hz WQXGA touch display\u003c/a\u003e that makes it look like you’re holding a small monitor instead of a portable console. It’s powered by an AMD Ryzen 8040HS processor, 16GB of RAM, and has detachable controllers with Hall effect joysticks. It’s also got a built-in kickstand so you don’t have to strain your arms by always playing it handheld. It will be available starting in Q2 2025 and start at $1,099.99.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/5/24335612/belkin-stage-powergrip-battery-pack-camera-grip-stand\"\u003eBelkin Stage PowerGrip\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Zoom\" tabindex=\"0\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Picture of Belkin PowerGrip attached to an iPhone with a second iPhone plugged into the PowerGrip’s USB-C Port\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 744px\" srcset=\"https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/376x212/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 376w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/384x216/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 384w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/415x233/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 415w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/480x270/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 480w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/540x304/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 540w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/640x360/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 640w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/750x422/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 750w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/828x466/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 828w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/1080x608/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 1080w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/1200x675/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 1200w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/1440x810/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 1440w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/1920x1080/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 1920w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/2048x1152/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 2048w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/2400x1350/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png 2400w\" src=\"https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2000x1125/2400x1350/filters:focal(1000x563:1001x564):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25816335/CTA003_PowerGrip_blue_2.png\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\"/\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Belkin\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eYour smartphone may take great pictures, but it lacks the refined ergonomics of a traditional camera. \u003ca href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/5/24335612/belkin-stage-powergrip-battery-pack-camera-grip-stand\"\u003eBelkin’s new Stage PowerGrip\u003c/a\u003e addresses that issue and battery anxiety. It’s a MagSafe power bank with a 10,000mAh battery, a retractable USB-C cable, and a design that adds a camera-like grip to the iPhone. It’s even got a physical shutter button that works with the iOS camera app over Bluetooth and a small LCD screen on the front showing the battery’s remaining charge. Pricing and availability haven’t been announced, but the PowerGrip will come in several color options.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
